How to Convert PDF to PowerPoint on EasePDF With EasePDF, you can convert PDF to a PowerPoint in three simple steps with ease, just like any other conversion on this website. No matter you’re a pro or a newbie on PDF, you won’t get it wrong! Now let’s see how it works.  Step 1. Upload your PDF file. Go to the EasePDF homepage, and select PDF to PPT converter. Hit the “Add File(s)” button to upload the PDF document from your local device, or just select the target PDF on your device then drop it to the upload area. If the PDF files you want to convert is on your cloud drives like Google Drive or Dropbox, you can import them to EasePDF by clicking the cloud drive’s icon as well.  Please note: EasePDF supports batch conversion for free, so you can upload multiple PDF files at the same time.  Step 2. Convert PDF to PowerPoint. Once your PDF file is uploaded, EasePDF will automatically start converting PDF to PowerPoint, just wait for seconds. The processing time depends mainly on the size of the PDF file you added. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-3096224744043987" src="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Processing-1024x597.png" alt="" width="660" height="385" srcset="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Processing-1024x597.png 1024w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Processing-300x175.png 300w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Processing-768x448.png 768w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Processing-30x18.png 30w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Processing.png 1102w" sizes="(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px" />  Step 3. Download the converted PowerPoint File. While the conversion process finishes, EasePDF will provide you a download link on the result page. To save it to your local device, you can directly click the “Download” button and the converted PowerPoint document will be immediately downloaded. You can also export it to your Google Drive and Dropbox. To share the download link with others, just click on the “Link” icon below and the link URL will be copied.  <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-3096224744043986" src="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Download-1024x597.png" alt="" width="660" height="385" srcset="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Download-1024x597.png 1024w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Download-300x175.png 300w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Download-768x448.png 768w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Download-30x18.png 30w, https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-PDF-to-PowerPoint-Download.png 1104w" sizes="(max-width: 660px) 100vw, 660px" />  Please note: The download link of your converted PPT will be invalid after 24 hours, please download it before it’s permanently deleted from the server.  What EasePDF Can Do For You EasePDF is an online PDF service that offers more than 20 online tools for PDF converting, creating and editing. You can convert PDF to other document formats including Word, Excel, PowerPoint, HTML, TXT, and RTF, and to image formats like JPG, PNG, GIF, and BMP. Vice versa, EasePDF can help you convert those file formats to create PDFs as well. Moreover, EasePDF also provides editing tools like PDF Editor, PDF Compressor, PDF Merger, PDF Splitter, etc. <img class="alignnone size-large wp-image-3096224744043984" src="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-Homepage-1024x600.png" alt="EasePDF Homepage" width="660" height="387" srcset="https://www.newsday.co.zw/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/EasePDF-Homepage-1024x600.png 1024w, https://www.newsd